ok lets explain databases 
databases is collecting and organizing data ,so that is easy to exract useful information from it . databases can store information about people, products,requests, etc.,and retrieve them whenever you want to analyze them and convert them
the importance of databases:
1-storing a huge amount of data with different types (texts-numbers-dates)
2-performing operation and processingon this data to get out with information
3-ease of retrieving information quickly and highly efficiently 
4- the ability to amend and update this data 
5-Achieve a high degree of security and confidentiality of the stored information and keep  It has tampering data  
6-centralizing data and limiting its frequency so that all data are dealt with

